パッケージ com.shimizukenta.secs.gem

インタフェース DynamicCollectionEvent

public interface DynamicCollectionEvent
This interface is implementation of Enable-CEID in GEM (SEMI-E30).

To get alias, alias()
To get CEID, collectionEventId()
To S2F37 Single CEID, toS2F37CollectionEvent()

Instances of this class are immutable.
